WEBVTT

00:00:00.209 --> 00:00:03.879
Why don't you take the afternoon off?
You deserve it.

00:00:03.963 --> 00:00:05.922
Spend it with that pretty wife of yours.

00:00:06.049 --> 00:00:09.051
Oh, shit, I forgot, she phoned last night.

00:00:10.219 --> 00:00:12.054
What'd you tell her?

00:00:12.138 --> 00:00:14.931
That you were probably
walking on the beach.

00:00:15.058 --> 00:00:16.141
I was.

00:00:16.225 --> 00:00:18.477
I guessed right then, didn't I?

